  <brief_title>A Study of the Safety and Efficacy of Posaconazole Versus Voriconazole for the Treatment of Invasive Aspergillosis (MK-5592-069)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 3 Randomized Study of the Efficacy and Safety of Posaconazole Versus Voriconazole for the Treatment of Invasive Aspergillosis in Adults and Adolescents (Phase 3; Protocol No. MK-5592-069)</official_title>
